===[a:method] メソッド定義

例:

          def fact(n)
            if n == 1 then
              1
            else
              n * fact(n-1)
            end
          end

文法:

#@since 2.1.0
          def メソッド名 ['(' [arg0 ['=' default0]] ... [',' '*' rest_args [, post ...]] [',' key1: [val1]] ... [',' '**'kwrest] [',' '&' block_arg]`)']
#@else
          def メソッド名 ['(' [arg0 ['=' default0]] ... [',' '*' rest_args [, post ...]] [',' key1: val1] ... [',' '**'kwrest] [',' '&' block_arg]`)']
#@end
